{"tid":2172233,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全球首例】港大證實男子外遊後二次感染　康復者非終身免疫","createTime":"2020-08-24T12:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T13:54:00.000Z","uid":369741,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb4d25c7e885346a0b93649be9bdba869368d70","tid":2172233,"uid":369741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:44:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=402967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402967&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=fa4c5dfd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402967&h=bf460829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=402967</a><br />\n<br />\n//33歲男患者三月底確診新冠病毒，四月中康復出院，他本月初獨自去旅行，經英國到西班牙，旅行完回港在機場做病毒檢測，結果呈陽性。他是「復陽」抑或再感染？//<br />\n<br />\n//港大微生物學系進行研究，透過次世代高通量基因測序，發現他第一次與第二次感染病毒株基因排序明顯不同，兩次的病毒證實他是再感染，是全球首宗人類重複感染新冠病毒的病例。研究團隊成員指，研究顯示康復者不是終身免疫。//<br />\n<br />\n//<span class=\"red\"><strong>外國曾提倡大部分人感染後，產生「群體免疫」作為防疫措施，杜啟泓指，今次研究顯示「群體免疫」是不切實際。</strong></span>//"},{"pid":"03d3b55e174de1edae073a03a6fe7335e3107f82","tid":2172233,"uid":29802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"仲去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff24e7438d4854d7584d0378e6c4347b71c212fc","tid":2172233,"uid":369741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03d3b55e174de1edae073a03a6fe7335e3107f82","tid":2172233,"uid":29802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"仲去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"唔知驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真抵死"},{"pid":"b38996f56f609a09996f72deab70b9585b5f99fe","tid":2172233,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":